title: The Crawling Eye (1958) 84 min.DVDRip Classic Sci-Fi Forrest Tuc
description:
The Crawling Eye AKA The Trollenberg Terror:  

Malevolent invaders from another world, cloak themselves within a radio-active
cloud high atop a Swiss mountain.

Trivia:
For its release in America the film was cut down to 75 minutes, because American 
distributors wanted to get to the monsters faster. The full running length of the 
film is 84 minutes and is fully restored on the DVD release
